name: Send form submission with required fields missing
fullName: Send form submission with required fields missing

steps.name: When I click on the "Submit button"
Then I receive the required message in the "First Name"
assert expected **<input#firstName>** to exist in the DOM
And I receive the validation message "First name is required" in the "First Name"
assert expected **<div#firstNameError.error>** to have text **First name is required**
Given I write "Test" in the "First Name"
When I click on the "Submit button"
Then I receive the required message in the "Last Name"
assert expected **<input#lastName>** to exist in the DOM
And I receive the validation message "Last name is required" in the "Last Name"
assert expected **<div#lastNameError.error>** to have text **Last name is required**
Given I write "Test" in the "Last Name"
When I click on the "Submit button"
And I receive the required message in the "Email Address"
assert expected **<input#email>** to exist in the DOM
And I receive the validation message "Email is required" in the "Email Address"
assert expected **<div#emailError.error>** to have text **Email is required**
Given I write "test@company.com" in the "Email Address"
When I click on the "Submit button"
And I receive the required message in the "Message"
assert expected **<textarea#message>** to exist in the DOM
And I receive the validation message "Message is required" in the "Message"
assert expected **<div#messageError.error>** to have text **Message is required**
